{code}
$ cat pyarrow/plasma_store 
#!/home/antoine/miniconda3/envs/pyarrow/bin/python
# EASY-INSTALL-ENTRY-SCRIPT: 'pyarrow','console_scripts','plasma_store'
__requires__ = 'pyarrow'
import re
import sys
from pkg_resources import load_entry_point

if __name__ == '__main__':
    sys.argv[0] = re.sub(r'(-script\.pyw?|\.exe)?$', '', sys.argv[0])
    sys.exit(
        load_entry_point('pyarrow', 'console_scripts', 'plasma_store')()
    )
{code}

So the entry point is executing itself endlessly...
